      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though a close inspection reveals minor rock chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical marks of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light cosmetic creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced religiously every 5,000 miles, with a recent professional inspection confirming that the transmission shifts smoothly and the engine pulls strong without hesitation. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. If you are looking for a reliable, honest car that looks great in a driveway and performs reliably on long commutes, this is it.",
      "price": 34500.0,
