      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience that meets our rigorous standards for quality and mechanical integrity. We invite discerning buyers to appreciate its well-preserved aesthetics and robust operational profile.",
      "price": 34500.0,
